THIS CONSULTING AGREEMENT (the "Agreement") dated on {{doc.agreement_date}}

{{doc.client}} (the "Client")
-AND-
Vertex Consulting & Compliance Pty Ltd of U30, 22-30 Wallace Avenue Point Cook, Victoria, 3030(the "Consultant").

BACKGROUND:

  1. The Client has approached the Consultant to assist with registration with NDIS Commission setting up of business in Disability sector.
  2. The Consultant is agreeable to providing such consulting services to the Client on the terms and conditions set out in this Agreement.
